
Unicode string library - Ustring
--------------------------------
Version 0.01. Copyright (C) 2010-2012 David Broman

The Ustring library is a simple library for adding unicode capability to
the OCaml language. It is designed to work in a similar manner as the 
standard String module, but with Unicode instead of ASCII.

Documentation
-------------
Module documentation is provided under directory "/doc". 

Contact
-------
If you have an comments or suggestions, please send an email
to David Broman, david@bromans.com

